sql:
SELECT log_id, starttime, seconds, ttime, status
FROM performance_logs
WHERE ttime = (SELECT MAX(ttime) FROM performance_logs);

external_knowledge:
- Critical metrics are those identified by the "is_critical" flag being 1; 
- The threshold value is the maximum acceptable value for a metric; 
- Average CPU time is the mean value of CPU time used across all performance logs for a given metric.
